property.name: text
property.value: The once-beautiful city gates of Kinstown Harbor are now tarnished and crumbling. Will you enter the ruins?

property.name: text
property.value: Climb up to the cliffside village of Moorhaven?

property.name: text
property.value: Will you enter the Elvish town of Port Artha?

property.name: text
property.value: You stand at the entrance of the Goblin's Mountain Fortress. Horrific sights and smells await within, dare you enter?

property.name: text
property.value: You stand before Castle Bashgar, the capital of the Suvian Kingdom. Will you enter?

property.name: text
property.value: The sacred grounds of Ashvari have served as the burial grounds for the Suvian Kings for centuries. Dare you explore the Ashvari Crypts?

property.name: text
property.value: Through the swirling snow you perceive a large keep with tall, sheer walls coated in ice. Will you enter Rogaard Keep, last refuge of the Dwarves?

property.name: text
property.value: You stand before the mighty Vygurn Tower, a place of great mystery and intrigue. You are astonished to see that it is protected by no door, nor any guards. Step into Vygurn Tower?

property.name: text
property.value: On this island you find a bustling village, mostly occupied by merchants, sailors and buccaneers. Will you warily enter and peruse their wares?

property.name: text
property.value: An enormous blockade prevents your passage!

property.name: text
property.value: At the base of Mount Vezu, you find an entrance to a cavern. A sulfurous odor wells up from within. Will you steel your nerves and enter?

property.name: text
property.value: You are set upon by vicious snakes!
